obligations. Alabama Power will continue to provide site-specific estimates of the decommissioning costs and related projections of
funds in the external trust to the Alabama PSC and, if necessary, would seek the Alabama PSC's approval to address any changes in
a manner consistent with NRC and other applicable requirements.
